title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Fantasy 5' game
maintext:
SACRAMENTO (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday evening’s drawing of the California Lottery’s “Fantasy 5” game were:
22-24-25-32-33
(twenty-two, twenty-four, twenty-five, thirty-two, thirty-three)
Estimated jackpot: $76,000
¶ The numbers are listed in sequential order, but any combination wins.
